AB  - In the originally published article, there was a missing note regarding the corresponding author details on the title page of the PDF. This should read: “Send correspondence to Thomas J Chemmanur, thomas.chemmanur@bc.edu”. instead of “Send”.There was an error in the text of Proofs of Propositions 3 and 4. (pp.45-46): ‘If 0 &lt; x Prp ≤ M, x will be equal to the number of shares purchased by firm insiders from pessimistic current shareholders with belief θ. On the other hand, if −Ms ≤ x Prp &lt; 0, this…. ’ instead of ‘If 0 &lt; x ≤ M, x will be equal to the number of shares purchased by firm insiders from pessimistic current shareholders with belief θ. On the other hand, if Ms ≤ x &lt; 0, this…..’.
